quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,121,"Nibaboola mbu; “Khusuubile Nyasaye Omulesi webindu bioosi."
  7,122,"Nyasaye Omulesi wa Musa nende Haruni.""
  7,123,"Firaun naboola mbu; “Oh! Musuubile muye neshili okhubasubula? Toto, khuno nookhututa khwamututile mulitokho lino mbu kho murusiemo abamenyamwo, bene litokho. Kho, mwitsa okhulola."
  7,124,"Toto, ndilabateta emikhono chienyu buchiikha, khandi toto nditsa okhubabamba mweesi.""
  7,125,"Nibaboola mbu; “Toto efwe ewa Nyasaye wefu Omulesi niwakhulikalukha."
  7,126,"Ne ewe shiwalolakhwo libii liosiliosi khwifwe tawe halali mbu khusuubile ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wefu Omulesi olwa bikhuulile. Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khusundulekho obwifwili (okhwisumilisia), ne okhufwisie nikhuli abasalamu.""
  7,127,"Ne abakhongo mubandu ba Firaun nibaboola mbu; “Koo, olalekha Musa nende Abandu baye banyasie eshialo, ne bakhulekhe ewe nende abanyasaye bobo?” Naboola mbu; “Khwitsa okhwira abana babu Abasiani ne khulalekha abakhana, ne toto efwe khuli abaamani hekulu wabu.”"
  7,128,"Musa naboolela Abandu bebe mbu; “Sabe obukhoonyi khu Nyasaye mana mwifwile. Eshialo ni shia Nyasaye, alishichelamia wayenya atong’ekhwo mubasumba baye. Ne omumalilikho omulayi kuliba kwa balia baria Nyasaye."
  7,129,"Nibaboola mbu; “Khwawumisibwa noshili okhukhwitsila, nende khandi niwakhamala okhukhwitsila.” Musa naboola mbu; “Khaundi Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi alasishia omusuku wenyu, ne alabakhola enywe okhuba abaruchi ba eshialo shino kho alole shinga enywe mulakhola.”"
  7,130,"Ne toto khwahelesia Abandu ba Firaun eshinyasio khumika, nende khukhubalemelia ebiamo; mbu khobanyoole okhwitsulila."